text: "Western Stars" is a 2019 song by Bruce Springsteen and is the title track to his 19th studio album Western Stars. It went to number 87 in Ireland, number 4 in Portugal and number 41 on the Billboard Hot Rock & Alternative chart. ==References== Category:2019 songs Category:Folk rock songs Category:Soft rock songs Category:Bruce Springsteen songs
